                    <h2>REAL ESTATE</h2>
                    <h3>Rocky Ridge Homes for Sale</h3>
                    <p>Rocky Ridge is located on the western extreme of the city with Country Hills Boulevard bordering it on the northern side and the Crowchild Trail bordering its southern side.</p>
                    <p>The eastern and western sides are bordered by Rocky Ridge Road and Twelve Mile Coulee Road, respectively.</p>
                    <p>Rocky Ridge homes for sale fetch good prices mainly due to the overall location of the area. Due to its elevated positioning (1,265 meters), residents get to enjoy splendid views of the surrounding locations.</p>
